snippet.title: PSX Longplay [186] YoYos Puzzle Park
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: NPI

Released in Japan as Gussun Paradise


More than 4 hours of this annoying game! Here's why:

00:03:48 Nanoda paradise (1st run)
In this run I collected a few of the Gussuns, which gave me a bad ending

01:40:28 Another run through Nanoda Paradise levels where I collected the remaining Gussuns

Which led to:

02:53:53 Weird Paradise

Where I collected all the Gussuns in one run


04:30:46 Weird Paradise bad ending (if you fail to collect all the gussuns) -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
